    {
      "id": "legend",
      "type": "rectangle",
      "x": 60,
      "y": 1060,
      "width": 1840,
      "height": 200,
      "backgroundColor": "#fff9db",
      "strokeColor": "#e8590c",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "createdAt": "2026-04-12T12:54:00.566Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-04-12T12:54:00.566Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "legend-title",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 80,
      "y": 1075,
      "width": 800,
      "height": 28,
      "strokeColor": "#e8590c",
      "text": "KEY FINDINGS",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "createdAt": "2026-04-12T12:54:00.566Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-04-12T12:54:00.566Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "legend-1",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 80,
      "y": 1110,
      "width": 1800,
      "height": 20,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "text": "1. ASYMMETRY: Planning + Work agents spawn in workspace worktree → read workspace CLAUDE.md (System 1 + project overlay).  Specialists spawn in DEVROOT → read devroot CLAUDE.md.",
      "fontSize": 14,
      "createdAt": "2026-04-12T12:54:00.566Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-04-12T12:54:00.566Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "legend-2",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 80,
      "y": 1135,
      "width": 1800,
      "height": 20,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "text": "2. Claude Code auto-loads CLAUDE.md from cwd. Work agent's WORK template explicitly cats project CLAUDE.md too. Specialists never auto-see workspace CLAUDE.md — only via {{workspacePath}} explicit reads.",
      "fontSize": 14,
      "createdAt": "2026-04-12T12:54:00.566Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-04-12T12:54:00.566Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "legend-3",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 80,
      "y": 1160,
      "width": 1800,
      "height": 20,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "text": "3. PLANNING agent has NO planning-specific CLAUDE.md. It inherits the generic workspace one and gets PLANNING_PROMPT.md as initial-message file argument. This is the source of PAN-598 confusion.",
      "fontSize": 14,
      "createdAt": "2026-04-12T12:54:00.566Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-04-12T12:54:00.566Z",
      "version": 1
